grid 64 64

# Native streamed reconfiguration entry path.
mark 25 28 RECONF ROOT
mark 25 29 FIRST CHILD

# Streamed delta component used to grow 2-bit -> 3-bit, then return 3-bit -> 2-bit.
mark 32 34 187 CELL DELTA REGION

# Stable probe and application lanes used by the proof.
mark 5 8 LEFT INPUT LANE
mark 15 12 SUM LANE 0
mark 15 26 SUM LANE 1

# Final observed active output ports after the full run.
mark 63 16 RESULT OUT 0=1
mark 63 34 RESULT OUT 1=1
